{"id":39701,"date":"2023-04-05T12:23:52","date_gmt":"2023-04-05T08:23:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=39701"},"modified":"2023-04-05T12:23:52","modified_gmt":"2023-04-05T08:23:52","slug":"kitab-allah-intercedes","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/05\/kitab-allah-intercedes\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Quran: Book of Allah intercedes for its reciters"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Recite the Quran, for it is the most excellent intercessor on the Day of Resurrection. It will say: O Lord, adorn him with the noblest of ornaments! Thus, he will be adorned with the noblest of ornaments. It will say: O Lord, dress him in the noblest of garments! Thus, he will be dressed in the noblest of garments. It will say: O Lord, crown him with the noblest of crowns! O Lord, be pleased with him, for after Your pleasure there is nothing!<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 3354<\/p>\n<p>Grade:\u00a0<em>Hasan<\/em>\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Darani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0642\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0621\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0622\u0646\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0646\u0650\u0639\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u0641\u0650\u064a\u0639\u064f \u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u064